### Server-Side Pagination Patterns (CRITICAL — Panel Only)

**⚠️ IMPORTANT: All new panel list features (users, companies, etc.) MUST use server-side pagination for optimal performance. Website pages do not use this pattern.**

#### Backend API Response Structure

All paginated endpoints MUST return this exact structure:

```javascript
{
  data: [...],                    // Array of actual items
  links: {
    next: "url?page=2&limit=10",  // Next page URL (null if last page)
    prev: "url?page=1&limit=10"   // Previous page URL (null if first page)
  },
  meta: {
    current_page: 1,              // Current page number
    last_page: 10,                // Total pages available
    total: 100                    // Total items count
  }
}
```

